tool_description: OneNote is a popular note-taking tool that's available online and on many mobile and tablet platforms.
name: OneNote
title: OneNote

api_list.name: createGroupSection
api_list.description: Creates a new section in the specified section group on Microsoft OneDrive.

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: The id of the section group where you want to create the section.

api_list.name: createNotebook
api_list.description: Creates a new notebook for the user in Microsoft OneDrive.

api_list.name: createNotebookSectionGroup
api_list.description: Creates a new section group in the specified notebook.

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: The id of the notebook where you want to create the section group.

api_list.name: createPage
api_list.description: Creates a new page in the user's default section and notebook.

required_parameters.name: accessToken
required_parameters.description: A valid OAuth token provided to the app based on the user credentials and the user having authorized access.

api_list.name: createPageInSection
api_list.description: Creates a new page in the specified section.

required_parameters.name: sectionId
required_parameters.description: The id of section where the page is to be created.

required_parameters.name: accessToken
required_parameters.description: A valid OAuth token provided to the app based on the user credentials and the user having authorized access.

api_list.name: createSection
api_list.description: Creates a new section in the specified notebook on Microsoft OneDrive.

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: The id of the notebook where you want to create the section.

api_list.name: createSectionDefaultPage
api_list.description: Creates a new page in the specified section of the user's default notebook. If the section doesn't exist (or was renamed), the API will create the section.

required_parameters.name: sectionName
required_parameters.description: The name of the section in the default notebook to create this new page in, if the section does not already exist.

required_parameters.name: accessToken
required_parameters.description: A valid OAuth token provided to the app based on the user credentials and the user having authorized access.

api_list.name: createSectionGroup
api_list.description: Creates a new section group in the specified section group.

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: The id of the notebook where you want to create the section group.

api_list.name: deletePage
api_list.description: You can't recover deleted data, so be careful when using this method. Deleting pages using the API deletes them permanently. They are not added to the OneNote Recycle Bin.

api_list.name: getAllNotebooks
api_list.description: Gets all notebooks to which a user has access in Microsoft OneDrive. This includes notebooks that are both owned by and shared with the user.

optional_parameters.name: search
optional_parameters.description: Specifies the term or phrase to search for in the page title, page body, image alt text, and image OCR text.

optional_parameters.name: select
optional_parameters.description: Expression specifying the properties to return

optional_parameters.name: top
optional_parameters.description: Specifies to return only the first n results. Default is 20, maximum is 100.

optional_parameters.name: count
optional_parameters.description: Specifies to include the count of the returned collection.

optional_parameters.name: skip
optional_parameters.description: Specifies to skip the first n results, typically used for paging. Example: 5.

optional_parameters.name: orderBy
optional_parameters.description: Expression specifying order. Default is lastModifiedTime desc. Example: createdTime.

optional_parameters.name: expand
optional_parameters.description: Expression specifying the navigation properties to return inline.
